---
description: Python / FastAPI / ML conventions
globs: ["**/*.py"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Type hints on every function signature and return value. Assume mypy --strict.
- Pydantic models for all FastAPI request and response bodies.
- Wrap every external call (DB, Anthropic, Twilio, Resend, file IO) in try/except and surface a clear error. Never let exceptions bubble up as raw 500s.
- Pin every dependency in requirements.txt (e.g. fastapi==0.115.*). No unpinned installs.
- Pure, testable functions; side effects (network, disk) at the edges.
- logging module in committed code, not print.
